  "text": "A homology model of human AQP3 was generated using E. coli GlpF (PDB 1FX8) as template, using Swiss-Model [CITATION_1] . In silico mutagenesis was done using Swiss PDB Viewer 33 and the lowest energy amino acid sidechain conformer(s) were chosen in each case.",
